{"text": "This modern, designer-furnished 3-room apartment located on the 10th storey of the EUROPALACE building in Žilina offers stunning views of the Little Fatra and Martinky. The layout of the apartment is ideal for those who want to enjoy the benefits of a high position without overheating or needing air conditioning, as it has an east-facing living room with kitchen that provides beautiful vistas of the Žilina basin mountains. The bedroom is north-facing, preventing overheating and eliminating the need for air conditioning. The bathroom features a bidet shower by the toilet, underfloor electric heating, and a washing machine and dryer discreetly placed in the corner of the bathroom. The apartment has been meticulously designed to meet both functional and practical purposes, with high-quality materials used throughout. The entrance door is security and fire-resistant, and the hallway connects the living and sleeping areas of the apartment, including the bathroom and a small pantry."}
